question: Pariksha ka yeh hai maidan, Jahan hoti hai sabki pehchaan. Answer sheets aur papers yahan, Mujhe dhoondo yahin ke aas-paas.
Suraj ki roshni ka yeh hai ghar, Urja ka raaz yahan banta amar. Prakriti aur vigyaan ka sangam, Mujhe dhoondo jahan hota hai karam.
Buttons aur screens ka yeh jahaan, Code likhne ka yahan hai samaan. Technologies ka khel yahin, Mujhe dhoondo keyboard ke paas wahin.
Man aur bhavna ka yeh hai ghar, Yahan milta hai dimaag ka asar. Samajh ke baatein banate hain raah, Mujhe dhoondo jahan sochon ki baat hai khaas.
Naksha, globe aur sthalon ka mel, Dharti ka yeh gyaan hai khel. Pahadon aur nadiyon ka hota hai zikr, Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai sansar ka chitr.
Madad ka yeh hai ek aasan jariya, Sawalon ka yahan milta hai jawab kaariya. Mujhe dhoondo desk ke paas, Jahan har samasya ka hota hai samaadhaan khaas.
Yahan banti hai nayi soch ki duniya, Tools aur machines ka yeh hai gharuniya. Loha aur lakdi yahin karte kaam, Mujhe dhoondo jahan banti hai nayi shaam.
Pen, copy aur saaman ka yeh hai ghar, Yahan mile sab kuch jo chahiye har bar. Mujhe dhoondo jahan likhne ka raaz, Aur mile likhne ki har ek saaz.
Jahan ball aur net ka hota hai khel, Team ke saath banta hai mel. Uchhal kood aur shor yahan, Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai net ka samaan.
Urja aur pragati ka hai yeh nam, Business aur vikas ka yeh hai kaam. Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai naye sapno ka asar, Adani ka yeh hai ek naya ghar.
Yahan milti hai padhai ki raah, Madad yahan banati hai sabka saath. Sapne yahan lete hain unchi udan, Mujhe dhoondo jahan sapno ka milta hai daan.
Smart duniya ka yeh hai jahan, Sensors aur devices ka banta hai saman. Internet se judta hai yeh khel, Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai technology ka mel.
Chemical aur tools ka yeh ghar, Prayogon ka hota yahan asar. Science ki duniya yahin shuru, Mujhe dhoondo jahan lab ka hai khel puro.
Yahan likhi gayi safalta ki kahani, Jo log bane hain yahan ke maharani. Achievement aur awards ka yeh hai ghar, Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai safalta amar.
Machines aur engines ka yeh jahaan, Mechanics ke gyaan ka yahan hai saman. Mujhe dhoondo jahan tools aur models hain, Yahin milta hai engineering ka samadhan.
Bijli ke raaz ka yeh hai kendra, Circuits aur wires yahan milta hai mool mantra. Current aur voltage ka hota yahan kaam, Mujhe dhoondo jahan lights ka hota hai naam.
Robots aur codes ka hai yeh ghar, Innovation ka sapna yahan hota amar. Technology ke naye naye aayaam, Mujhe dhoondo jahan bante hain nayi kahaaniyan.
Practical aur projects ka yeh hai adda, Yahan milti hai knowledge ki masti aur gadda. Mujhe dhoondo jahan hai learning ka samaan, CPL1 lab ka yeh hai ek naya pehchaan.
Naye sapno ka yeh hai pravesh dwar, Admission ka yahan milta hai sansaar. Mujhe dhoondo jahan naye students ka hota hai saath, Admission Cell ke paas banti hai baat.
Dress aur uniform ka yeh hai mahal, Discipline ka hota yahan ek asal. Mujhe dhoondo jahan dress code ka hota hai paal, Uniform office ke paas hota hai saudaal.
Prem aur gyaan ka yeh hai sthaan, Yahan sabka hota hai sammaan. Jahan naam mein hai pyar aur gyaan, Mujhe dhoondo yahan ke paas asaan.
Khaane ka swad aur baatein yahan, Sabke chehre pe laye muskaan. Chai, samose aur doston ka mela, Mujhe dhoondo jahan khushiyon ka mela.
Duniya ka raaz yahan chhupa, Naksha aur sthalon ka bana hai rasta. Round aur map se jahan banti hai baat, Mujhe dhoondo jahan duniya ki baat.
Shuttle aur racket ka yeh hai khel, Chaal aur kood yahan milta hai mel. Net ke paar jit ka sapna, Mujhe dhoondo jahan khel hai apna.
Gyaan aur pragati ka yeh hai prateek, Sankalp aur utsah ka yeh hai deek. Mujhe dhoondo jahan soch badi ho, Vivekanand ke sang kuch nayi baat ho.
